        <div class="vak4-q-text">8. Meerwaarden op gebouwde onroerende goederen &ndash; gezamenlijk belastbaar:</div>
        <div class="vak4-col-duo">
            <div class="vak4-input-cell"><span class="vak2-code">1176-00</span><InputNumber @bind-Value="Data.Code1176" class="vak4-amount" /></div>
            <div class="vak4-input-cell"><span class="vak2-code">2176-00</span><InputNumber @bind-Value="Data.Code2176" class="vak4-amount" /></div>
